intro.title: Introduction to HAQQ L2
intro.description: HAQQ L2 is a scalable and interoperable Ethereum L2 blockchain built on the Optimism stack. This Layer 2 solution provides high performance and low fees for HAQQ Network users.

l2-network/contractaddress.title: Contract Addresses
l2-network/contractaddress.description: This page contains a comprehensive list of all deployed contracts in both L1 and L2 networks of HAQQ with their addresses and explorer links. The contracts are based on OP Stack v5.0.0 from the Ethereum Optimism repository and deployed using op-deployer v0.5.0-rc2.
